edu.cmu.cs.plural.annot
Enum Use

      edu.cmu.cs.plural.annot.Use
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Use>
public enum Use
extends java.lang.Enum<Use>

This enumeration distinguishes the allowed uses of a permission:

  • Dynamic dispatch (only): DISPATCH
  • Field access (only): FIELDS
  • Both: DISP_FIELDS
This is primarily interesting to distinguish receiver permissions of instance methods; permissions for other objects are usually (implicitly) dispatch-only. All permissions can be passed into private methods since these are statically dispatched.

Mar 25, 2009
